        h1 Style &amp; Content
        p.lead Styles for displaying content with some of the most commonly used HTML elements, including normalization, typography, images, tables, and more.

    main.main-container.styleguide-container(role='main')
      .container
        .row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-3.col-sm-last
            .page-header
              include ./layout/_style-nav.pug

          .col-xs-12.col-md-9

            h2.page-header Table
            p
              :markdown

                For basic styling — light padding and only horizontal dividers — add the base class `.table` to a `<table>`.

            table.table
              thead
                tr
                  th Member
                  th Organisation
                  th Role
                  th Action

              tbody
                include molecules/table-prototype-1
                include molecules/table-prototype-2
                include molecules/table-prototype-3
                include molecules/table-prototype-4
                include molecules/table-prototype-5

            pre
              code.language-markup.
                <table class="table">
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th>Member</th>
                      <th>Organisation</th>
                      <th>Role</th>
                      <th>Action</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>

                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <div class="media">
