            h2.page-header Table scroll/swipe
            p To allow smooth interaction with bigger and more complex tables we make use of the
             a(href='https://github.com/filamentgroup/tablesaw') Tablesaw library.
            p
              :markdown
                Add classes `.table` and `.tablesaw` to the table element.
                To allow the user to use the swipe gesture (or use the left and right buttons) to navigate the columns you need to add the following attribute `<table data-tablesaw-mode="swipe">`.

                To lock (prevent from scrolling) the first column you can use `data-tablesaw-priority="persist"` attribute on the `<th>` element like `<data-tablesaw-priority="persist">`. It is not recommended to use this on other columns or multiple columns as this will cause problems on small devices.

                To a add a mini map use `<table data-tablesaw-mode="swipe" data-tablesaw-minimap>`.

            table.table.tablesaw.tablesaw-swipe(data-tablesaw-mode="swipe", data-tablesaw-minimap)
              thead
                tr
                  th(data-tablesaw-priority="persist") Member
                  th Organisation
                  th Role
                  th Action

              tbody
                include molecules/_member1-table-view.pug
                include molecules/_member2-table-view.pug
                include molecules/_member3-table-view.pug
                include molecules/_member4-table-view.pug
                include molecules/_member5-table-view.pug
                include molecules/_member1-table-view.pug
                include molecules/_member2-table-view.pug
                include molecules/_member3-table-view.pug
                include molecules/_member4-table-view.pug
                include molecules/_member5-table-view.pug
            pre
              code.language-markup.
                <table data-tablesaw-mode="swipe" data-tablesaw-minimap class="table tablesaw">
                  <thead>
                    <tr>
                      <th data-tablesaw-priority="persist">Member</th>
                      <th>Organisation</th>
                      <th>Role</th>
                      <th>Action</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="tablesaw-cell-persist">
                        <div class="media media-middle">
                          <div class="media-left"><a href="my-stream.html"><img src="assets/content/images/member-table-view-5.jpg"></a></div>
                          <div class="media-body"><a href="my-stream.html">John Johnson</a></div>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <td>Receptionist at Bastion Hotels</td>
                      <td>Member</td>
                      <td>
                        <div class="btn-group">
                          <button type="button" autocomplete="off" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm btn-raised dropdown-toggle">Manage<span class="caret"></span></button>
                          <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a href="#">Edit</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Remove</a></li>
                          </ul>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>

    include ./layout/_scripts.pug
